channel.title: EJEN ALI THE MOVIE
channel.desc: Twelve-year-old Ejen Ali, who works as a spy for a secret agency, MATA, discovers that MATA has now upgraded to a new device called IRIS Neo. However, this new invention leads Ali to question his place and usefulness to MATA. Risking his loyalty to MATA, Ejen Ali embarks on a dangerous course of action in an attempt to prove his value to MATA.

channel.title: MAYA THE BEE MOVIE
channel.desc: Buzz along with Maya, a curious baby bee so excited about life that she keeps breaking bee colony rules. When she learns that the bees are going to fight the hornets, she decides to act.
